comments: Johnson (TOR) establishes himself in a screening position in Beasley's (MIN) path and absorbs the contact.
Davis (TOR) makes marginal contact with Rubio's (MIN) body that does not affect Rubio's SQBR.
Towns (MIN) brushes Davis' (TOR) back as he extends his arm while setting the pick and marginal contact occurs.
Towns (MIN) and Powell (TOR) make incidental contact with each other following the pass by Powell.
Towns (MIN) firms up in a screening position in Bembry's (TOR) path and does not deliver contact.
Towns (MIN) extends his leg into VanVleet's (TOR) lower body while setting the screen and affects his ability to defend.
Beasley (MIN) lifts and switches his pivot foot.
Towns (MIN) commits a take foul on Davis (TOR).
Towns (MIN) establishes himself in a screening position in the path of Powell (TOR) and absorbs the contact.
VanVleet (TOR) commits a take foul on Rubio (MIN).
